at-posing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Doja-Cat-posing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Doja-Cat-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Doja-Cat-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Doja-Cat-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/doja-cat">Doja Cat</a>分享了由克里斯蒂娜·里奇 (Christina Ricci) 主演的单曲《恶魔》的视频，并公布了她即将发行的专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/doja-cat-announces-new-album-scarlet-3490730">Scarlet</a> 》的更新封面。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/doja-cat-planet-her-review-2978431">Doja Cat – “Planet Her”评论：备受争议的流行说唱歌手进入她的帝国阶段</a></strong></li></ul><p>这段视频由 Doja Cat 和<a class="external-link" href="https://christianbreslauer.com/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener" data-offer-url="https://christianbreslauer.com/" data-event-click="{&quot;element&quot;:&quot;ExternalLink&quot;,&quot;outgoingURL&quot;:&quot;https://christianbreslauer.com/&quot;}" data-uri="52c7c9d4e7461184ff3c9af396a20959">Christian Breslauer</a>共同执导，将这位艺术家描绘成一个长着黑色角和红色眼睛的恶魔，在天花板上爬行，而里奇则躺在床上，在漆黑的暴风雨之夜抬头仰望。</p><p>视频中的一个场景向斯坦利·库布里克 1980 年的电影<em>《闪灵》</em>致敬，其中多贾猫坐在浴缸里，黑色液体溢出，一只黑爪手抓住了说唱歌手的后脑勺。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Doja Cat - 恶魔（官方视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/qwtyEKTGGQ8?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> 《恶魔》是 Doja Cat 即将于 9 月 22 日发行的第四张录音室专辑《Scarlet》中发行的第三首单曲。这首歌曲是继之前发行的单曲《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/doja-cat-returns-with-new-song-and-video-paint-the-town-red-3478155">Paint The Town Red</a> 》和《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/doja-cat-unveils-her-next-single-attention-in-creepy-video-teaser-3456527">Attention</a> 》之后发行的。</p><p>这位说唱歌手还透露了《Scarlet》的更新封面<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/doja-cats-new-album-has-near-identical-artwork-to-german-metal-band-chaver-3491636">，因为人们发现她的专辑封面与德国金属乐队 Chaver 几乎相同</a>，后者将于同一天发行最新专辑。</p><p>她的第一幅作品是一只紫粉色的蜘蛛，上面有一滴血。 Doja Cat took to social media on Tuesday (August 29) to share the sleeve, but it was soon revealed that Chaver&#39;s new album artwork for their record &#39;Of Gloom&#39; – revealed on July 29 and also due for release on September 22 – is almost exactly the same, except for the shape of the blood droplet and the positioning of the spider&#39;s legs. Both of the art pieces were created by the same artist, Dusty Ray.</p><p> The updated cover now features a pair of arachnids with pink pearl bodies locking their mouths together. </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CwnYD_wrXu6/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fil